## Attribution Requirements

When sharing or adapting content from this platform, you must:

1. Provide the name "MathEdu" as the original source
2. Link to the original repository: https://github.com/[your-username]/[repository-name]
3. Indicate if you made any changes to the original content
4. Include this license notice

**Example Attribution:**
```
Based on content from MathEdu (https://github.com/[your-username]/[repository-name])
Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
```

